        * fallbacks for json import
        * improved HTTP error handling
        * unit tests
        
        0.2.0 (2010-06-27)
        -------------------
        * add cli client to send notifications
        
        0.1.1 (2010-06-25)
        -------------------
        * fix typo which prevented proper function call of subscribe_user
        
        0.1.0 (2010-06-17)
        -------------------
        * add basic API access
        
